    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="text-center mb-12">
          <span class="inline-block px-4 py-2 bg-primary-100 text-primary-800 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold mb-4">
            The Challenge
          </span>
          <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
            Why Corporate Relocation Is a <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-600 to-primary-700 bg-clip-text text-transparent">Challenge</span>
          </h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">
            Employee mobility requires expert coordination across immigration, housing, family needs, and compliance
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-50 to-white p-8 rounded-2xl border border-gray-100">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-500 to-primary-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Complex Compliance Requirements</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
              Relocating employees to Switzerland involves complex immigration (work permits, visas, quota management), tax implications (cross-border taxation, social security), housing regulations (lease guarantees, landlord requirements), and family considerations (school applications, spouse work permits). Missing any compliance step risks delays, penalties, or failed relocations.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-50 to-white p-8 rounded-2xl border border-gray-100">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-500 to-primary-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">HR Policy Consistency & Budget Control</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
              HR departments struggle maintaining consistent relocation policies across employee levels (executives vs mid-level vs entry), controlling costs (housing budgets, school fees, travel expenses), ensuring equitable treatment, and tracking spending. Without standardized processes and vendor agreements, costs spiral and employee satisfaction varies widely creating HR headaches.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-50 to-white p-8 rounded-2xl border border-gray-100">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-500 to-primary-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 4.354a4 4 0 110 5.292M15 21H3v-1a6 6 0 0112 0v1zm0 0h6v-1a6 6 0 00-9-5.197M13 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Family Integration & Employee Retention</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
              Corporate relocations fail when families don't integrate successfully. Spouse career challenges, children's school placement difficulties, cultural isolation, and lack of social networks cause early departures. Companies lose ROI on relocation investment (CHF 20,000-100,000+ per employee) plus recruitment costs and knowledge loss when families struggle to settle. Family support is critical for retention.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-50 to-white p-8 rounded-2xl border border-gray-100">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-500 to-primary-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 21V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v16m14 0h2m-2 0h-5m-9 0H3m2 0h5M9 7h1m-1 4h1m4-4h1m-1 4h1m-5 10v-5a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v5m-4 0h4" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Multi-Vendor Management Complexity</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
              Companies often coordinate separate vendors for immigration (lawyers), housing (real estate agents), schools (education consultants), moving (logistics), and settling-in (various local providers). Multiple vendors mean inconsistent service quality, communication gaps, no single point of contact, duplicated efforts, and confusion for employees. Having the right relocation agency partner streamlines the entire process with coordinated service delivery.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-12 p-8 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-50 via-white to-red-50 rounded-2xl border-2 border-primary-100">
          <div class="flex items-start">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-primary-600" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M18 10a8 8 0 11-16 0 8 8 0 0116 0zm-7-4a1 1 0 11-2 0 1 1 0 012 0zM9 9a1 1 0 000 2v3a1 1 0 001 1h1a1 1 0 100-2v-3a1 1 0 00-1-1H9z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="ml-4">
              <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Expert Insight</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
                <strong>Without professional relocation agency support, companies often:</strong> Experience failed relocations costing CHF 50,000-150,000+ in wasted investment, suffer employee early departures due to poor family integration, face compliance violations and immigration penalties, lose control over relocation budgets, and damage employer brand with inconsistent experiences. The right agency partner ensures smooth transitions, happy employees, controlled costs, and successful long-term retention. ReloFinder helps you find that perfect agency match.
