            ReloFinder connects you with relocation agencies providing comprehensive employee mobility services
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-gray-100 hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300">
            <div class="flex items-start">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-500 to-primary-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-lg">
                  1
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="ml-6">
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Relocation Policy & Package Design</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
                  Agencies help HR teams design comprehensive relocation policies including tiered service packages (executive, mid-level, entry), budget frameworks by employee level, service scope definition (core vs optional services), vendor SLA standards, cost control mechanisms, and compliance requirements. Policy design ensures consistency, fairness, and predictable costs across all employee relocations.
                </p>
                <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                  <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-primary-50 text-primary-700 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">Policy Design</span>
                  <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-primary-50 text-primary-700 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">Package Tiers</span>
                  <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-primary-50 text-primary-700 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">Budget Control</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-gray-100 hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300">
            <div class="flex items-start">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-500 to-primary-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-lg">
                  2
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="ml-6">
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Housing, Immigration & Education Coordination</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
                  Complete relocation services including work permit and visa applications, housing search with budget negotiation, international school search and applications, family settling-in support (registration, bank accounts, utilities), cultural orientation and language lessons, spouse career support, and ongoing assistance. Single point of contact coordinates all services seamlessly.
                </p>
                <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                  <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-primary-50 text-primary-700 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">Work Permits</span>
                  <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-primary-50 text-primary-700 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">Housing Search</span>
                  <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-primary-50 text-primary-700 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">School Placement</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-gray-100 hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300">
            <div class="flex items-start">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-500 to-primary-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-lg">
                  3
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="ml-6">
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Vendor Management & Service Level Agreements</h3>
