                  Agencies manage all sub-vendors (immigration lawyers, real estate agents, movers, schools) under unified SLAs ensuring consistent quality, response times, and service standards. HR teams get single invoice consolidation, transparent pricing, quality assurance, escalation procedures, and performance metrics. No more juggling multiple vendors and invoices.
                </p>
                <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                  <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-primary-50 text-primary-700 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">SLA Management</span>
                  <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-primary-50 text-primary-700 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">Quality Control</span>
                  <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-primary-50 text-primary-700 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">Single Invoice</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-gray-100 hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300">
            <div class="flex items-start">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0">
                <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-500 to-primary-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-lg">
                  4
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="ml-6">
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">Reporting, Compliance & Cost Control</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">
                  Comprehensive reporting dashboards showing relocation pipeline status, budget vs actual spend tracking, service delivery metrics, employee satisfaction scores, and compliance audit trails. Agencies provide quarterly business reviews, cost optimization recommendations, policy refinement suggestions, and benchmarking against industry standards. Complete transparency for HR and finance teams.
                </p>
                <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                  <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-primary-50 text-primary-700 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">Dashboards</span>
                  <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-primary-50 text-primary-700 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">Budget Tracking</span>
                  <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-primary-50 text-primary-700 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">Compliance</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 text-center">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
