  </section>

  <section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-50 via-white to-primary-50">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <span class="inline-block px-4 py-2 bg-primary-100 text-primary-800 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold mb-4">
            Regional Focus
          </span>
          <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
            Corporate Relocation Across <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-600 to-primary-700 bg-clip-text text-transparent">Switzerland</span>
          </h2>
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-600">
            Different Swiss cities attract different types of corporate relocations and multinational operations
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-gray-100 overflow-hidden hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300">
            <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-600 to-primary-700 p-6">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Zürich</h3>
              <p class="text-primary-100">Financial Hub, High Executive Mobility</p>
            </div>
            <div class="p-8">
              <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                Zurich attracts the highest volume of executive and senior management relocations in Switzerland. Major banks (UBS, Credit Suisse), insurance companies (Zurich Insurance, Swiss Re), and tech firms (Google, Meta) maintain significant operations. High demand for international schools, luxury housing, and white-glove relocation services. Agencies must handle complex tax planning and premium housing searches.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-gray-100 overflow-hidden hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300">
            <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-600 to-primary-700 p-6">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-2">Geneva</h3>
              <p class="text-primary-100">Diplomatic, NGO & International Organizations</p>
            </div>
            <div class="p-8">
              <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                Geneva specializes in diplomatic and NGO relocations with unique requirements including UN staff, WHO employees, and international organization transfers. Requires expertise in G permit applications, international school admissions (competitive waiting lists), and French language integration. Corporate relocations often focus on luxury goods, private banking, and commodity trading sectors with multilingual support essential.
